{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10107949716418-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10107949716418-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100108278031","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096571382","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096585685","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096586764","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096653599","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000672366","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100120601254-1"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读语段，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":360,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">祖母死了，我就跟祖父学诗。因为祖父的屋子空着，我就闹着一定要睡在祖父那屋里。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">早晨念诗，晚上念诗，半夜醒了也是念诗。念了一阵，念困了再睡去。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">祖父教我读《千家诗》，但没有课本，全凭口头传诵，祖父念一句，我就念一句。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">祖父说：“少小离家老大回……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">我也说：“少小离家老大回……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">都是些什么字，什么意思，我不知道，只觉得念起来那声音很好听。所以很高兴地跟着喊。我喊的声音，比祖父的声音更大。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">我一念起诗来，我家的五间房里的人都可以听见，祖父怕我喊坏了喉咙，常常警告我说：“房盖被你抬走了。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">听了这笑话，我笑了一会儿，过不了多久，就又喊起来了。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">夜里我也是照样地喊，母亲吓唬我，说再喊她要打我。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">祖父也说：“没有你这样念诗的，你这不叫念诗，你这叫乱叫。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">但我觉得这乱叫的习惯不能改，若不让我叫，我念它干什么。每当祖父教我一首新诗，一开头我若听了不好听，我就说：“不学这个。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">祖父于是就换一首，换一首不好，我还是不要。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">春眠不觉晓，处处闻啼鸟。夜来风雨声，花落知多少。”这一首诗，我很喜欢，我一念到第二句，“处处闻啼鸟”那“处处”两字，我就高兴起来了。觉得这首诗，实在是好，真好听！“处处”该多好听。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">还有一首我更喜欢的：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">重重叠叠上瑶台，</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">几度呼童扫不开。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">刚被太阳收拾去，</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">又教明月送将来。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">就这“几度呼童扫不开”，我根本不知道什么意思，就念成“西沥忽通”扫不开。越念越觉得好听，越念越有味。</span></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>最初“我”是怎样跟祖父学诗的？（　）</p><p>①祖父念一句，我就念一句。</p><p>②不是念诗，而是喊诗。</p><p>③按照课本读诗。</p><p>④学什么诗全凭我的兴趣，只念读起来声音好听的诗。</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"①②③","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"①②④","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"②③④","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]}]},"docId":"Q_10107949716418","version":1,"wordId":null,"pictureUrl":null,"tagId":null,"createdAt":1500178695834,"deletedAt":null,"olCreatedAt":1500897190164,"olUpdatedAt":1515302124467,"sentenceIds":null,"sentenceContents":null,"practiceTypeIds":